        <updateDate>2022-11-07T15:13:36Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Defense Domestic Producers Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill adds certain items (e.g., armor on tactical ground vehicles) to the list of high priority goods and services that require review and analysis by the Department of Defense (DOD) in order to develop appropriate actions related to procurement and sourcing. DOD must also consider producers in the United States when reviewing the specified items to determine and develop appropriate actions related to restricting procurement.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
